text: "Over My Head" is a 1975 song by British American band Fleetwood Mac and taken from their 10th studio album Fleetwood Mac. It went to number 20 in the United States and number 9 in Canada. It was their first song to reach the Billboard Hot 100 since Oh Well in 1969. ==References== Category:1975 songs Category:Fleetwood Mac songs
title: Over My Head (Fleetwood Mac song)
